1. Python Version Required is 3.9.13.
2. Install and add tesseract.exe in system path to use pytesseract library. Download link: https://github.com/UB-Mannheim/tesseract/wiki
3. Run `pip install -r .\requirements.txt --dry-run --ignore-installed` and check if all the packages are compatible with your system. If not, install the compatible versions of the packages.
4. Run `pip install -r .\requirements.txt` to install all the required packages.
5. Install Protobuf additionally with `pip install protobuf==3.20.3`.          
6. To Run the Project , goto ./src/ and enter `python main.py` , enter username to register FACE , make sure you are in a proper lighting condition.
7. If Face isnt authenticated properly then quit and Run `python main.py -fd`, to run project without FACE AUTH.
